OL,6,FA man has admitted threatening a
OL,7,Fteenage girl with a gun following a
OL,8,Fcampaign of grooming and sexual abuse
OL,9,Fin the 2000s.
OL,11,FChristopher Oates, 44, is the first
OL,12,Foffender to be convicted as part of
OL,13,Fwide-ranging investigations into
OL,14,Fhistorical child sexual abuse in
OL,15,FManchester in the 2000s.
OL,17,FOates coerced one of his victims to
OL,18,Fbelieve he was her boyfriend when she
OL,19,Fwas just 14. He would subject her to
OL,20,Fsex work and sell her to other men.
