OL,6,FThe court heard evidence of how Oates,
OL,7,Ffrom Stockport and nicknamed 'Nails'
OL,8,Fdue to his long fingernails, groomed
OL,9,Fthe girls and preyed on their
OL,10,Fvulnerability.
OL,12,FOates pleaded guilty on the fourth day
OL,13,Fof his trial at Manchester Crown
OL,14,FSquare Crown Court to three offences.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Eleanor
OL,17,FHumphrey's, senior investigating
OL,18,Fofficer for this case, said: "I am so
OL,19,Fpleased for both women that they have
OL,20,Ftoday finally got some justice all
OL,21,Fthese years after this horrific abuse.
