OL,6,F"Christopher Oates is a depraved and
OL,7,Fmanipulative paedophile. The abuse he
OL,8,Fsubjected these two girls to was
OL,9,Fhorrific. He was even prepared to try
OL,10,Fand deny this throughout a trial and
OL,11,Fmake the victims relive it all over
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,14,F"Thankfully, due to the weight of
OL,15,Fevidence against him, his crimes have
OL,16,Ffinally caught up with him two decades
OL,17,Flater. This is all thanks to the brave
OL,18,Fand compelling testimony from the
OL,19,Fvictims, who now have been spared the
OL,20,Fexperience of being cross-examined in
OL,21,Fcourt."
