OL,7,FParker, our lead for public protection
OL,8,Fand vulnerability said: "Today is a
OL,9,Fsignificant day for GMP and its
OL,10,Fongoing pursuit of justice for victims
OL,11,Fof non-recent child sexual abuse.
OL,13,F"Firstly, I commend the bravery of the
OL,14,Fvictims and the meticulous dedication
OL,15,Fof the investigation team and support
OL,16,Fservices. Together, long-awaited
OL,17,Fjustice has been secured.
